WEBVTT

00:07.420 --> 00:10.620
CHELSEA: First box goes in my car, the other in the truck.

00:12.880 --> 00:14.720
Guess that's it.

00:14.720 --> 00:16.090
You got everything?

00:16.090 --> 00:17.560
I think so.

00:17.560 --> 00:18.900
I, uh, left the house keys

00:18.900 --> 00:20.430
and the garage clicker by the nightstand.

00:20.430 --> 00:22.080
Thanks.

00:22.450 --> 00:25.440
so you still plan to...move in with your dad?

00:25.480 --> 00:26.630
Just for a while.

00:27.440 --> 00:30.660
- You gonna be okay? - Me? Oh, yeah, yeah.

00:30.690 --> 00:32.750
I mean, I am gonna miss the cat.

00:33.400 --> 00:35.230
You hate Sir Lancelot.

00:35.270 --> 00:37.780
I did at first, but over time I came to find...

00:37.820 --> 00:39.230
Yeah, you're right. I hate that thing.

00:40.640 --> 00:42.690
I put in a change of address at the post office,

00:42.730 --> 00:45.190
but here's my dad's address just in case.

00:45.220 --> 00:47.250
I might be open to a trade.

00:47.280 --> 00:49.610
I'll keep the cat, you take Alan.

00:49.640 --> 00:51.400
Still got his carrier.

00:52.270 --> 00:53.820
Take care of yourself, Charlie.

00:53.850 --> 00:55.300
You do the same.

00:58.850 --> 01:01.710
I'm sorry it didn't work out.

01:01.740 --> 01:03.500
Me, too.

